    <string name="setup_instructions">• Pick your real browser below (for example, Chrome).\n• Turn on Enabled and Clean clicked links.\n• Tap Open default apps settings and set Sanity as your default browser.\n\nAfter that, tap links in WhatsApp, Gmail, SMS, and other apps. Sanity opens briefly, removes trackers, forwards the link to your browser, then exits.\n\nTo clean a copied URL, use Share on the text or link, choose Sanity, then pick where to send the cleaned link. It does not run in the background.</string>
